reviewText: I have found nothing of interest in this book at all, but this is my personal view Not impressed at all

Steve continues to produce solid, worthy, products.  He cuts through the fluff and provide useful information.  I am a great fan of his material, just wish I could get through the Reiki Master process.

Hi

I pre-ordered this DVD off Steve Murray's Web site and I'm very happy with it. It fills in the gaps in my Reiki knowledge. I wish this DVD was available when I first started Reiki. I would recommend the DVD to a Reiki healer, or any person beginning Reiki or thinking about beginning Reiki.
